@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

    The new user announcer door writes a PUBLIC mail message to
    everyone, telling them that a new user has joined the BBS, and
    to reply (to the sysop) if they know the user.

@EndNode

@Node Installation "Installation"

  Installation
  ============

    This is included in the default setup of HydraBBS V1.03.

    The door is stored as:

    HBBS:Doors/System/NewUserAnnouncer/NewUserAnnouncer.HBBS

    Add the following lines to a Commands/System file (HBBS:Commands/System is
    recommended).

    NewUserAnnouncer_Type_1=HBBS
    NewUserAnnouncer_Door_1=HBBS:Doors/System/NewUserAnnouncer/NewUserAnnouncer.HBBS {N} {O}

    Add the following @^@ item to your "Joined" special screens
    (e.g. HBBS:Screens/Special/Joined.TXT)

    @^SYSDOOR^NEWUSERANNOUNCER@

    See HBBS:Storage/Example_Screens/Special/Joined.TXT for an example.

    Edit the config file:

    HBBS:Doors/System/NewUserAnnouncer/NewUserAnnouncer.CFG

@EndNode

